{"tid":287801,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"窮遊英國，搭咩航空好？","createTime":"2017-06-17T16:52:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-18T06:16:19.000Z","uid":64322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"03ac0b841cd5211f03441090ddc285dd0e1ec754","tid":287801,"uid":64322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T16:52:05.000Z","msg":"小弟打算九月左右去英國見識下<br />\n但又budget唔多 盡可能揀六千內來回機票<br />\n見越南航空都係四千幾 係胡志明市等七個鐘再轉機 <br />\n有冇巴絲打搭過越航 或者可以比啲建議小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51c10372b5486efadbc7b912a21c3ecb9635a712","tid":287801,"uid":27939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T16:56:02.000Z","msg":"中東三寶有offer既話其實幾好，都係4000幾<br />\n建議畀多幾百出境留2-3日<br />\n好值得去"},{"pid":"e4482d5d5b47dc93aec1e4f76b5780ac2d812af7","tid":287801,"uid":27939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T16:57:33.000Z","msg":"留意返中東三寶因為平會有d大陸人<br />\n提早check in 揀d走廊位，唔好坐最前同最後呢d近廁所既"},{"pid":"1c5692b8f684bec35e560f28d3a008ac7289fe48","tid":287801,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T17:01:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中東三寶有offer既話其實幾好，都係4000幾<br />\n建議畀多幾百出境留2-3日<br />\n好值得去</blockquote><br />\n即係轉機果陣出境兩三日？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5782bf2ec5066933dfb31bfcc8d377f629f1ac53","tid":287801,"uid":9466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T17:04:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中東三寶有offer既話其實幾好，都係4000幾<br />\n建議畀多幾百出境留2-3日<br />\n好值得去</blockquote><br />\n杜拜就可能係，多哈嗰啲就算啦"},{"pid":"610639690398aae23a1243d77504723f6ff85564","tid":287801,"uid":64322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T17:06:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留意返中東三寶因為平會有d大陸人<br />\n提早check in 揀d走廊位，唔好坐最前同最後呢d近廁所既</blockquote><br />\n我都睇過三寶 都要過六千 可能仲未有優惠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果平都想去見識下 咁大個